  <!-- Our Story -->
  <section class="about-section" role="region" aria-labelledby="story-title">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 id="story-title" class="section-title">Our Story</h2>
      <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <div style="background: linear-gradient(145deg, #111111, #0c0c0c); border-radius: 12px; padding: 40px; border-left: 4px solid #00ff7f;">
          <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #b0b0b0;">
            ToolNest began with a simple observation: people everywhere struggle to find the right words for special occasions. Whether it's a birthday, anniversary, festival, or personal milestone, the pressure to create the "perfect message" can be overwhelming.
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #b0b0b0;">
            Our founder, a digital creator passionate about both technology and human connection, saw an opportunity to bridge this gap. What started as a single birthday wish generator has grown into a comprehensive hub of specialized tools, each designed with care to address specific emotional expressions.
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #b0b0b0;">
            Today, ToolNest is part of a family of free online tools that includes <a href="https://onlinewebtool.live/" target="_blank">OnlineWebTool</a> and <a href="https://onlinetoolstack.site/" target="_blank">OnlineToolStack</a>, serving millions of users worldwide who trust us to help them communicate better.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

